burnEeus(address,uint256,int256).notice: burns carbons by resizing EEUs, and/or removing EEUs from the _ledger. removes EEUs (or fractions thereof) from the main list and from the _ledger, resizing as necessary. the supplied _ledger owner must hold the supplied quantity of carbon in aggregate across _ledger EEUs, and of the supplied type.
